{"word":"G4789 - συγκληρονόμος - synklēronómos - soong-klay-ron-om'-os - Fellow -heir","slug":"G4789","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκληρονόμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>synklēronómos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soong-klay-ron-om'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Fellow -heir"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03B3;&#x03BA;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - sugkle&#x0304;ronomos</b> - <i>soong-klay-ron-om'-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2818\">G2818</a>; a <i>co-heir</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>participant in common:</i> - fellow (joint) -heir, heir together, heir with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4776\">G4776</a>, <a href=\"#/G4800\">G4800</a>, <a href=\"#/G4806\">G4806</a>, <a href=\"#/G4821\">G4821</a>, <a href=\"#/G4832\">G4832</a>, <a href=\"#/G4833\">G4833</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>, <a href=\"#/G4854\">G4854</a>, <a href=\"#/G4855\">G4855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G4888\">G4888</a>, <a href=\"#/G4891\">G4891</a>, <a href=\"#/G4916\">G4916</a>, <a href=\"#/G4957\">G4957</a>"}]}